global_attributes.comment: Deployment summary: Deployment summary: This glider was deployed to the Frontal Zone 2 (FZ-2) line 2019-06-18T23:36:35 UTC and recovered 2019-06-26T18:45:00 UTC. The glider began exhibiting communication issues and could not hold an Iridium phone call shortly after deployment so it was recovered early for troubleshooting.
